name: Predator Cybercats - Pantera
description: This black panther is the undefeated champion on a brutal planet named Kito known for it's harsh living environment and raiding tribes. Pantera rules all with an iron fist and a steel gaze capable of turning foes to stone. Ability to conceal the sound of his footsteps. Double armor plated exterior many have tried to take this champion down and have failed. Strong silent type, cool and collected, strikes when you least expect it.
